#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn40.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga "
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Catutthajhānapañhāsutta → upekkhāsuttaṃ (bj) | upekkhako (pts1)
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Catutthajhānapañhāsutta "
msgstr "4. A Question About the Fourth Absorption "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn40.4:1.1"
msgid "“‘Catutthaṃ jhānaṃ, catutthaṃ jhānan’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘fourth absorption’. "

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho catutthaṃ jhānanti? "
msgstr "What is the fourth absorption? "

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi: "
msgstr "It occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.4"
msgid "‘idha bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "‘It’s when, giving up pleasure and pain, and ending former happiness and sadness, a mendicant enters and remains in the fourth absorption, without pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness. "

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati catutthaṃ jhānan’ti. "
msgstr "This is called the fourth absorption.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.4:1.6"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "And so … I was entering and remaining in the fourth absorption. "

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato sukhasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. "
msgstr "While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by pleasure beset me. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.266, sc2
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said, "

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna. "
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna! "

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.3"
msgid "Mā, brāhmaṇa, catutthaṃ jhānaṃ pamādo, catutthe jhāne cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, catutthe jhāne cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, catutthe jhāne cittaṃ samādahā’ti. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect the fourth absorption, brahmin! Settle your mind in the fourth absorption; unify your mind and immerse it in the fourth absorption.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.4"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. "
msgstr "And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the fourth absorption. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya … pe … mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti. "
msgstr "So if anyone should be rightly called a disciple who attained to great direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

